Activate venv
-------------
python -m venv venv

venv\Scripts\activate

install fastapi
---------------
pip install fastapi uvicorn sqlalchemy pymysql python-dotenv

install jwt
-----------
pip install python-jose

install cryptography
--------------------
pip install cryptography
Fernet.generate_key()

Create requirement file
-----------------------
pip freeze > requirements.txt
pip install requirements.txt

Create Windows Service
----------------------
Open Command Prompt in Administrator mode
sc delete FastAPIService

Create new:
sc create FastAPIService binPath= "cmd /c D:\PBL\MTH\backend\start_fastapi.bat" start= auto

Then Start:
sc start FastAPIService

Using NSSM:
Download nssm.zip:
Extract in C:\nssm
cd c:\nssm\win64\
nssm install FastAPIService
    Application Path:python.exe
    Startup Directory: C:\WEB\PBL
    Arguments: run.py

net start PBLFastAPIService
net stop PBLFastAPIService
netstat -ano | findstr :4000
